io.confluent.ksql.test.parser

Class TestStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.test.parser.TestStatement

  • public final class TestStatement
extends java.lang.Object
    A single line of a test execution. A TestStatement can consist of either:
    • a KsqlParser.ParsedStatement, which will issue an update to the ksqlDB, or
    • an AssertStatement, which will ensure data is accurate, or
    • a TestDirective, which will ensure some metadata on the test
